[
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">When <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> had <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">gone</st> a <st data-num=\"04592\" class=\"\">short way</st> beyond the <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">summit</st>, <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st> the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">servant</st> of <st data-num=\"04648\" class=\"\">Mephibosheth</st> was <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">there</st> to <st data-num=\"07122\" class=\"\">meet</st> him. He had a <st data-num=\"06776\" class=\"\">couple</st> of <st data-num=\"02543\" class=\"\">donkeys</st> that were <st data-num=\"02280\" class=\"\">saddled</st>, and <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> them were <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">200</st> <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">loaves of bread</st>, <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">100</st> <st data-num=\"06778\" class=\"\">raisin cakes</st>, <st data-num=\"03967\" class=\"\">100</st> <st data-num=\"07019\" class=\"\">baskets of summer fruit</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and a <st data-num=\"05035\" class=\"\">container</st> of <st data-num=\"03196\" class=\"\">wine</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559 0413\">asked</st> <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> did you bring <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these things</st>?\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cThe <st data-num=\"02543\" class=\"\">donkeys</st> are for the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> to <st data-num=\"07392\" class=\"\">ride on</st>, the <st data-num=\"03899\" class=\"\">loaves of bread</st><n id=\"2\" /> and the <st data-num=\"07019\" class=\"\">summer fruit</st> are for the <st data-num=\"05288\" class=\"\">attendants</st> to <st data-num=\"0398\" class=\"\">eat</st>, and the <st data-num=\"03196 \">wine</st> is for those who get <st data-num=\"03287\" class=\"\">exhausted</st> in the <st data-num=\"08354 04057\">desert</st>.\u201d<n id=\"3\" /> ",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">asked</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0346\" class=\"\">Where</st> is your <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">master\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">grandson</st>?\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201cHe <st data-num=\"02009 03427\">remains</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> he <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u2018<st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">Today</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> will <st data-num=\"07725\" class=\"\">give back</st> to me my <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">grandfather\u2019s</st><n id=\"3\" /> <st data-num=\"04468\" class=\"\">kingdom</st>.\u2019\u201d ",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"02009 03605\">Everything</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">that</st> was <st data-num=\"04648\" class=\"\">Mephibosheth\u2019s</st> now belongs to you.\u201d <st data-num=\"06717\" class=\"\">Ziba</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st>, \u201cI <st data-num=\"07812\" class=\"\">bow</st> before you. May I <st data-num=\"04672\" class=\"\">find</st> <st data-num=\"02580\" class=\"\">favor</st> in your <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st>, my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0935 05704\">reached</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0980\" class=\"\">Bahurim</st>. <st data-num=\"02009 08033\">There</st> a <st data-num=\"0376 03318\">man</st> from <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04940\" class=\"\">extended</st> <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">family</st> <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">named</st> <st data-num=\"08096\" class=\"\">Shimei</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"01617\" class=\"\">Gera</st> <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">came out</st>, <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">yelling curses</st> as he <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">approached</st>.<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "He <st data-num=\"05619\" class=\"\">threw</st> <st data-num=\"068\" class=\"\">stones</st> <st data-num=\"05619\" class=\"\">at</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> of <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">King</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st>, as well as <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">and</st> the <st data-num=\"01368\" class=\"\">soldiers</st> who were on his <st data-num=\"03225\" class=\"\">right</st> and on his <st data-num=\"08040\" class=\"\">left</st>. ",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "As he <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">yelled curses</st>, <st data-num=\"08096\" class=\"\">Shimei</st> <st data-num=\"03541 0559\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Leave</st>! <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">Leave</st>! You <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> of <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">bloodshed</st>, you <st data-num=\"01100\" class=\"\">wicked</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"07725 05921\">punished</st> you for<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">spilled blood</st> of the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">house</st> of <st data-num=\"07586\" class=\"\">Saul</st>, in <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whose</st> <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">place</st> you <st data-num=\"04427\" class=\"\">rule</st>. Now the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">given</st> the <st data-num=\"04410\" class=\"\">kingdom</st> into the <st data-num=\"03027\" class=\"\">hand</st> of your <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>. <st data-num=\"07451\" class=\"\">Disaster</st> has <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">overtaken</st> you, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> <st data-num=\"0859\" class=\"\">you</st> are a <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">man</st> of <st data-num=\"01818\" class=\"\">bloodshed</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st> of <st data-num=\"06870\" class=\"\">Zeruiah</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> should <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"04191\" class=\"\">dead</st> <st data-num=\"03611\" class=\"\">dog</st> <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">curse</st> my <st data-num=\"0113\" class=\"\">lord</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>? <st data-num=\"04994\" class=\"\">Let</st> me <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">go over</st> and <st data-num=\"05493\" class=\"\">cut off</st> his <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">head</st>!\u201d ",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "But the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> do we have in common,<n id=\"1\" /> you <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">sons</st> of <st data-num=\"06870\" class=\"\">Zeruiah</st>? <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">If</st> he <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">curses</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">because</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> to him, \u2018<st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">Curse</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st>!,\u2019 <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">who</st> can <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st> to him, \u2018<st data-num=\"04069\" class=\"\">Why</st> have you <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">done</st> <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">this</st>?\u2019\u201d ",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "Then <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"052\" class=\"\">Abishai</st> and <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> his <st data-num=\"05650\" class=\"\">servants</st>, \u201cMy <st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">own</st> <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>, my <st data-num=\"0834 03318 04578\">very own flesh and blood</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> is <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">trying to take</st> my <st data-num=\"05315\" class=\"\">life</st>. <st data-num=\"0637 03588\">So also</st> <st data-num=\"06258\" class=\"\">now</st> this <st data-num=\"01145\" class=\"\">Benjaminite</st>! <st data-num=\"03240\" class=\"\">Leave</st> him <st data-num=\"03240\" class=\"\">alone</st> so that he can <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">curse</st>, <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">for</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">spoken</st> to him.",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0194\" class=\"\">Perhaps</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">notice</st> my <st data-num=\"06040\" class=\"\">affliction</st><n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">day</st> <st data-num=\"07725 03068\">grant</st> me <st data-num=\"02896\" class=\"\">good</st> in <st data-num=\"08478\" class=\"\">place</st> of his <st data-num=\"07045\" class=\"\">curse</st>.\u201d<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">So <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> and his <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">went</st> on their <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st>. But <st data-num=\"08096\" class=\"\">Shimei</st> kept <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">going</st> along the <st data-num=\"06763\" class=\"\">side</st> of the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">hill</st> <st data-num=\"05980\" class=\"\">opposite</st> him, <st data-num=\"07043\" class=\"\">yelling curses</st> as he <st data-num=\"05619\" class=\"\">threw</st> <st data-num=\"068 05980\">stones</st> <st data-num=\"06080\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">dirt</st> at them.<n id=\"1\" />",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "The <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st> and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">who</st> were <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> <st data-num=\"05889\" class=\"\">exhausted</st> at their destination, <st data-num=\"08033\" class=\"\">where</st> David<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05314\" class=\"\">refreshed</st> himself.</p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Now when <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> and <st data-num=\"03605 05971\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st><n id=\"1\" /> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">arrived</st> in <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>,<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"0302\" class=\"\">Ahithophel</st> was <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him.",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"01961 0834\">When</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"07463\" class=\"\">friend</st> <st data-num=\"02365\" class=\"\">Hushai</st> the <st data-num=\"0757\" class=\"\">Arkite</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">came</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, <st data-num=\"02365\" class=\"\">Hushai</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">him</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">Long live</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>! <st data-num=\"02421\" class=\"\">Long live</st> the <st data-num=\"04428\" class=\"\">king</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\"><st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"02365\" class=\"\">Hushai</st>, \u201cDo you call <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">this</st> <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">loyalty</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">to</st> your <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">friend</st>? <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">didn\u2019t</st> you <st data-num=\"01980\" class=\"\">go</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> your <st data-num=\"07453\" class=\"\">friend</st>?\u201d ",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"02365\" class=\"\">Hushai</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">No</st>, I will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">be</st> <st data-num=\"0854 03427\">loyal</st> to the one <st data-num=\"03588 0834\">whom</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>, <st data-num=\"02088\" class=\"\">these</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>, and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> the <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">men</st> of <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> have <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">chosen</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> ",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"08145\" class=\"\">Moreover</st>, <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whom</st> should <st data-num=\"0589\" class=\"\">I</st> <st data-num=\"05647\" class=\"\">serve</st>? Should it <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">be</st> his <st data-num=\"01121\" class=\"\">son</st>? Just <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> I <st data-num=\"05647 06440\">served</st> your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>, <st data-num=\"03651\" class=\"\">so</st> I will <st data-num=\"01961 06440\">serve</st> you.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /></p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">Then <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">said</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"0302\" class=\"\">Ahithophel</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"03051\" class=\"\">Give</st> us your <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">advice</st>. <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> should we <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">do</st>?\u201d ",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<st data-num=\"0302\" class=\"\">Ahithophel</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">replied</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">to</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">Sleep</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"1\" /> your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06370\" class=\"\">concubines</st> <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">whom</st> he <st data-num=\"03240\" class=\"\">left</st> to <st data-num=\"08104\" class=\"\">care for</st> the <st data-num=\"01004\" class=\"\">palace</st>. <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st> will <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st> <st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> you have made yourself <st data-num=\"0887\" class=\"\">repulsive</st> <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">to</st> your <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father</st>. Then your <st data-num=\"03027 03605 0834 0854\">followers</st> will be <st data-num=\"02388\" class=\"\">motivated to support</st> you.\u201d<n id=\"2\" />",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "So they <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">pitched</st> a <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tent</st> for <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"01406\" class=\"\">roof</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> and <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">slept</st> <st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">with</st><n id=\"2\" /> his <st data-num=\"01\" class=\"\">father\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06370\" class=\"\">concubines</st> in the <st data-num=\"05869\" class=\"\">sight</st> of <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "2 Samuel",
    "chapter": "16",
    "text": "<p class=\"bodytext\">In <st data-num=\"01992\" class=\"\">those</st> <st data-num=\"03117\" class=\"\">days</st> <st data-num=\"0302\" class=\"\">Ahithophel\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"06098 0834 03289\">advice</st> was considered as valuable <st data-num=\"0834\" class=\"\">as</st> a <st data-num=\"07592 0376 01697 0430\">prophetic revelation.</st><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">Both</st> <st data-num=\"01732\" class=\"\">David</st> <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">and</st> <st data-num=\"053\" class=\"\">Absalom</st> <st data-num=\"03651 03605\">highly regarded</st> the <st data-num=\"06098\" class=\"\">advice</st> of <st data-num=\"0302\" class=\"\">Ahithophel</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  }
]